{"tid":2253170,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一名六歲小一女學生 今早在校門口被淋紅油","createTime":"2020-10-22T03:49:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T05:31:23.000Z","uid":22556,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"5266d487528b83e54cfb790e54ab8c5a632d28c2","tid":2253170,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T03:49:32.000Z","msg":"上午8時許，一名小學女生正前往大圍美林邨東華三院蔡榮星小學上學，抵達學校門外時，突然被人淋潑紅油，其右手被紅油染紅，兇徒逞兇後逃去，校方職員見狀報警。<br />\n<br />\n事主年約6歲，就讀該校小一。據知，她返抵校門外時，一名沒有戴口罩的男子突然出現向她淋潑油漆，逞兇後往美林商場逃去。田心分區刑事調查隊第8隊正追緝年約30至40歲、身高約5.5呎、身穿全身黑色衫褲、沒有戴口罩的中國籍男子。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20201022/s00001/1603330540046/%e5%a4%a7%e5%9c%8d%e5%b0%8f%e5%ad%b8%e5%a5%b3%e7%94%9f%e6%a0%a1%e9%96%80%e5%a4%96%e9%81%ad%e6%b7%8b%e7%b4%85%e6%b2%b9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20201022%2Fs00001%2F1603330540046%2F%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e5%259c%258d%25e5%25b0%258f%25e5%25ad%25b8%25e5%25a5%25b3%25e7%2594%259f%25e6%25a0%25a1%25e9%2596%2580%25e5%25a4%2596%25e9%2581%25ad%25e6%25b7%258b%25e7%25b4%2585%25e6%25b2%25b9&d=mhl3ai6H9Odyk596tiaOPcg1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=29fae4be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20201022%2Fs00001%2F1603330540046%2F%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e5%259c%258d%25e5%25b0%258f%25e5%25ad%25b8%25e5%25a5%25b3%25e7%2594%259f%25e6%25a0%25a1%25e9%2596%2580%25e5%25a4%2596%25e9%2581%25ad%25e6%25b7%258b%25e7%25b4%2585%25e6%25b2%25b9&h=ab12a72f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20201022/s00001/1603330540046/%e5%a4%a7%e5%9c%8d%e5%b0%8f%e5%ad%b8%e5%a5%b3%e7%94%9f%e6%a0%a1%e9%96%80%e5%a4%96%e9%81%ad%e6%b7%8b%e7%b4%85%e6%b2%b9</a>"},{"pid":"d0b27b7abca2c6756057919c8ddcf0dbb67d6f6c","tid":2253170,"uid":367967,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T03:50:41.000Z","msg":"陰公豬<img 